            <h2>About Our Clinic</h2>
            <p>Welcome to <span class="clinic-name">Serenity Health Clinic</span>, where compassionate care meets advanced medical expertise. Our clinic has been serving the community for years, providing top-tier healthcare services with a patient-centered approach.</p>

